@node "wn" "What's New"

* New since version 1.6

More countries!  Added French, Italian, German, Swedish, Star Wars and
NASCAR versions

More options!  Added the following options;

   Quick Start - Eack player gets 2 properties at the start.

   Fast Play - Eliminates most delays in games for quicker action.

   Bankrupt To Bank - Bankrupt player's props go back to bank
                      instead of being auctioned.

   Ownership Indicators - Shows who owns what property without having
                          to use the menus.

